Package: braid
Maintainer: Andrie de Vries <andrie@pentalibra.com>
License: GPL (>=2)
Title: A report writing system that creates and compiles
    LaTEX and pdf output
LazyData: true
LazyLoad: true
Author: Andrie de Vries <andrie@pentalibra.com>
Description: This package tries to solve the problem of
    writing simple reports in R, without having to learn
    LaTEX and SWeave first.  At the moment it supports
    creation of PDF files via LaTEX only.
Author@R: person("Andrie", "de Vries",
    email="andrie@pentalibra.com")
Version: 0.1-06
URL: https://github.com/andrie/braid
Date: 2012-06-25
ByteCompile: yes
